1
00:00:36,700 --> 00:00:42,060
=Twin Fire Dawn=

2
00:00:42,100 --> 00:00:45,060
=Episode 10=

3
00:00:58,900 --> 00:01:00,019
(This jade pendant...)

4
00:01:00,020 --> 00:01:05,489
笙ｪLove is so strange,
the way it entangles me笙ｪ

5
00:01:05,490 --> 00:01:08,259
笙ｪI still haven't awakened笙ｪ

6
00:01:08,260 --> 00:01:09,620
(Zhuang Yunqiu...)

7
00:01:10,580 --> 00:01:11,999
(Could it really be you?)

8
00:01:12,000 --> 00:01:16,049
笙ｪStill gently holding onto the笙ｪ

9
00:01:16,050 --> 00:01:20,239
笙ｪA happy game that began within a dream笙ｪ

10
00:01:20,240 --> 00:01:23,549
(Three years ago)

11
00:01:23,550 --> 00:01:29,690
笙ｪCan you still see it within the night?笙ｪ

12
00:01:30,660 --> 00:01:31,570
Who's there?

13
00:01:36,070 --> 00:01:41,460
笙ｪForcing me to trade pain for the past笙ｪ

14
00:01:41,620 --> 00:01:44,259
笙ｪIn this world笙ｪ

15
00:01:44,260 --> 00:01:44,820
You...

16
00:01:45,340 --> 00:01:46,420
Are you alright?

17
00:01:47,980 --> 00:01:49,580
Who sent you here?

18
00:01:50,420 --> 00:01:51,939
No one sent me.

19
00:01:51,940 --> 00:01:53,820
I just came here to sketch.

20
00:01:54,020 --> 00:01:56,059
But the snow blocked the roads.

21
00:01:56,060 --> 00:01:58,500
If I hadn't come here, I wouldn't
have been able to make it home.

22
00:02:01,060 --> 00:02:01,740
You...

23
00:02:02,380 --> 00:02:03,900
Are you alright?

24
00:02:04,820 --> 00:02:06,500
There are so many dead bodies here.

25
00:02:07,460 --> 00:02:08,739
Aren't you scared?

26
00:02:08,740 --> 00:02:10,299
Of course I'm scared.

27
00:02:10,300 --> 00:02:11,500
But you...

28
00:02:11,580 --> 00:02:12,340
You...

29
00:02:14,100 --> 00:02:16,020
Let me help you.

30
00:02:19,820 --> 00:02:20,900
No need.

31
00:02:21,540 --> 00:02:22,740
Really no need?

32
00:02:29,060 --> 00:02:29,740
You...

33
00:02:30,740 --> 00:02:31,899
Are you alright?

34
00:02:31,900 --> 00:02:32,899
Wake up.

35
00:02:32,900 --> 00:02:33,580
Hey!

36
00:02:34,940 --> 00:02:36,100
Is anyone there?

37
00:02:36,220 --> 00:02:37,460
Anyone?

38
00:02:56,220 --> 00:02:57,060
There.

39
00:02:57,860 --> 00:02:59,220
Don't worry too much.

40
00:02:59,300 --> 00:03:00,700
I read in a book before

41
00:03:00,740 --> 00:03:03,660
that your condition
is only temporary vision loss

42
00:03:03,740 --> 00:03:05,619
caused by trauma to the head.

43
00:03:05,620 --> 00:03:07,580
As long as you rest for a while,
you'll recover.

44
00:03:07,780 --> 00:03:09,779
But during this time,
you can't look at bright light,

45
00:03:09,780 --> 00:03:10,620
understand?

46
00:03:20,220 --> 00:03:21,220
What are you doing?

47
00:03:21,540 --> 00:03:23,220
Don't be so tense.

48
00:03:23,540 --> 00:03:25,180
Your wound is still bleeding.

49
00:03:25,340 --> 00:03:26,500
I'll help wipe it clean.

50
00:03:43,500 --> 00:03:46,580
笙ｪWhat is there to seek or desire笙ｪ

51
00:03:46,630 --> 00:03:49,190
笙ｪTrapped in worldly sorrow笙ｪ

52
00:03:50,060 --> 00:03:51,380
Thank you for saving me, Miss.

53
00:03:52,500 --> 00:03:53,700
What's your name?

54
00:03:53,940 --> 00:03:55,220
My name is Zhuang Yunqiu.

55
00:03:55,260 --> 00:03:56,140
What about you?

56
00:03:56,350 --> 00:03:58,339
笙ｪYour silhouette笙ｪ

57
00:03:58,340 --> 00:03:59,499
My name is Gu Nianchi.

58
00:03:59,500 --> 00:04:02,099
笙ｪCarved through endless hardship笙ｪ

59
00:04:02,100 --> 00:04:02,739
I'll remember it.

60
00:04:02,740 --> 00:04:08,230
笙ｪLove and longing
traced through countless lifetimes笙ｪ

61
00:04:08,990 --> 00:04:11,739
笙ｪFates intertwined笙ｪ

62
00:04:11,740 --> 00:04:12,679
Then I'll get going now.

63
00:04:12,679 --> 00:04:15,100
笙ｪRight and wrong no longer clear笙ｪ

64
00:04:15,400 --> 00:04:16,920
The snow only stopped a short while ago.

65
00:04:17,000 --> 00:04:18,320
The mountain paths are dangerous.

66
00:04:18,780 --> 00:04:20,060
Why don't you stay here instead?

67
00:04:20,300 --> 00:04:23,739
It's alright. I'm going to pick some wild fruit
for you. They're especially delicious.

68
00:04:23,740 --> 00:04:24,780
I'll be right back.

69
00:04:26,140 --> 00:04:27,740
I can go catch a mountain pheasant too.

70
00:04:27,780 --> 00:04:29,020
We can roast it and eat together.

71
00:04:29,740 --> 00:04:31,179
Your eyes haven't recovered yet.

72
00:04:31,180 --> 00:04:32,659
Wait until your eyes heal first.

73
00:04:32,660 --> 00:04:33,779
I'll go this time.

74
00:04:33,780 --> 00:04:35,780
I promise I'll be back soon.

75
00:04:36,100 --> 00:04:37,059
Then come back early.

76
00:04:37,060 --> 00:04:37,860
I'll wait for you.

77
00:04:38,740 --> 00:04:39,620
Got it.

78
00:04:41,110 --> 00:04:44,710
笙ｪSo called blame,
nothing more than an excuse笙ｪ

79
00:04:45,940 --> 00:04:47,660
(I never thought once you left,)

80
00:04:48,420 --> 00:04:50,260
(that would be
the last time we'd ever meet.)

81
00:04:50,710 --> 00:04:53,830
笙ｪI still long to hold you once again笙ｪ

82
00:04:54,620 --> 00:04:55,660
Yunqiu.

83
00:04:56,060 --> 00:04:57,020
Is that you?

84
00:04:57,060 --> 00:04:57,979
Shaoyuan, it's me.

85
00:04:57,980 --> 00:05:01,699
笙ｪLet the frost wither
the greenery beyond the window笙ｪ

86
00:05:01,700 --> 00:05:02,620
Cheng Yi.

87
00:05:03,620 --> 00:05:04,980
What happened to your eyes?

88
00:05:06,020 --> 00:05:07,820
It's nothing. Just a minor injury.

89
00:05:08,660 --> 00:05:09,500
Shaoyuan.

90
00:05:11,020 --> 00:05:12,460
Godmother, she...

91
00:05:16,320 --> 00:05:18,640
(Spirit tablet of our late mother, Lu Shuying)

92
00:05:20,180 --> 00:05:21,980
How could Mother have died from illness?

93
00:05:22,580 --> 00:05:23,940
Ever since you left,

94
00:05:24,980 --> 00:05:27,300
Godmother's health
kept getting worse by the day.

95
00:05:27,660 --> 00:05:29,140
And there was no money for treatment.

96
00:05:29,620 --> 00:05:31,340
How could there be no money?

97
00:05:31,580 --> 00:05:33,099
I sent money home every month.

98
00:05:33,100 --> 00:05:35,380
I told my brother to buy medicine
and supplements for Mother.

99
00:05:35,620 --> 00:05:37,459
After Gu Shaoyan received the money,

100
00:05:37,460 --> 00:05:38,740
he kept it all for himself.

101
00:05:38,820 --> 00:05:40,220
He spent recklessly every single day

102
00:05:40,500 --> 00:05:41,860
and never used any of it

103
00:05:42,060 --> 00:05:43,740
to treat Godmother.

104
00:05:44,260 --> 00:05:45,420
What did you say?

105
00:05:46,420 --> 00:05:48,720
A few days ago, Commander-in-Chief Li
came looking for you.

106
00:05:49,180 --> 00:05:50,740
He said his name was Gu Nianchi.

107
00:05:51,220 --> 00:05:52,860
He was promoted to Commander

108
00:05:53,260 --> 00:05:54,700
and left with Commander-in-Chief Li.

109
00:05:55,500 --> 00:05:57,020
The day he left,

110
00:05:57,380 --> 00:05:58,780
Godmother was already...

111
00:05:59,540 --> 00:06:00,900
Already at her last breath.

112
00:06:01,980 --> 00:06:04,180
Taking my place wasn't enough for him.

113
00:06:05,780 --> 00:06:09,580
He even ignored
his own mother's life and death.

114
00:06:10,300 --> 00:06:11,620
Not only that...

115
00:06:12,060 --> 00:06:12,860
He also...

116
00:06:14,580 --> 00:06:15,780
Just say it.

117
00:06:17,000 --> 00:06:19,560
He was afraid the truth about
taking your identity would be exposed,

118
00:06:20,180 --> 00:06:22,100
so he slaughtered everyone
in our village.

119
00:06:22,660 --> 00:06:26,300
To cover up what he'd done,
he even set the whole village on fire.

120
00:06:26,860 --> 00:06:30,900
I only survived because
I had come out to look for you.

121
00:06:32,100 --> 00:06:34,780
Gu Shaoyan.

122
00:06:46,340 --> 00:06:48,180
(Spirit tablet of our late mother, Lu Shuying)

123
00:06:56,000 --> 00:06:57,000
(Spirit tablets of our late mother, Lu Shuying
and our late father, Yiren)

124
00:07:12,220 --> 00:07:13,900
(My eyes have recovered.)

125
00:07:14,340 --> 00:07:15,460
(Don't worry.)

126
00:07:15,680 --> 00:07:18,820
(Once I finish what I need to do, I'll
definitely come to your house and marry you.)

127
00:07:20,860 --> 00:07:26,640
(Zhuang Residence)

128
00:07:26,760 --> 00:07:28,280
Why is there
an official seal on the gate?

129
00:07:28,300 --> 00:07:29,980
Nianchi, I've already
investigated everything.

130
00:07:30,260 --> 00:07:31,860
The Zhuang family was raided

131
00:07:32,340 --> 00:07:33,419
for selling opium.

132
00:07:33,420 --> 00:07:35,980
The entire household refused to confess,

133
00:07:36,380 --> 00:07:37,940
which led to a clash with the Commander.

134
00:07:38,020 --> 00:07:39,140
In the end,

135
00:07:39,900 --> 00:07:40,860
they were all executed.

136
00:07:42,340 --> 00:07:43,700
Executed by who?

137
00:07:44,420 --> 00:07:45,339
Your brother.

138
00:07:45,340 --> 00:07:46,580
Commander Gu Nianchi.

139
00:07:46,660 --> 00:07:47,300
No.

140
00:07:47,420 --> 00:07:48,580
Gu Shaoyan.

141
00:07:57,080 --> 00:08:00,880
(Zhuang Residence)

142
00:08:10,250 --> 00:08:15,630
笙ｪLove quietly hides within the wind笙ｪ

143
00:08:16,170 --> 00:08:21,510
笙ｪFalling into your smile before my eyes笙ｪ

144
00:08:22,200 --> 00:08:27,579
笙ｪStirring my dreams
and awakening my heart笙ｪ

145
00:08:27,580 --> 00:08:30,940
(I finally understand all the secrets
you've been hiding.)

146
00:08:35,300 --> 00:08:36,460
(From now on,)

147
00:08:36,620 --> 00:08:38,660
(let me be the one to protect you.)

148
00:08:39,670 --> 00:08:45,749
笙ｪI still haven't awakened笙ｪ

149
00:08:45,750 --> 00:08:49,589
笙ｪStill gently holding onto the笙ｪ

150
00:08:49,590 --> 00:08:54,189
笙ｪA happy game that began within a dream笙ｪ

151
00:08:54,190 --> 00:08:57,189
笙ｪJoy and pleasure笙ｪ

152
00:08:57,190 --> 00:09:03,239
笙ｪCan you still see it within the night?笙ｪ

153
00:09:03,240 --> 00:09:09,540
笙ｪThe life I long for
is tangled within it笙ｪ

154
00:09:09,690 --> 00:09:14,960
笙ｪForcing me to trade pain for the past笙ｪ

155
00:09:15,160 --> 00:09:18,020
笙ｪIn this world笙ｪ

156
00:09:26,780 --> 00:09:31,470
笙ｪHow can broken love ever go on?笙ｪ

157
00:09:32,780 --> 00:09:38,100
笙ｪHow much hope must fade into despair?笙ｪ

158
00:09:38,600 --> 00:09:42,180
笙ｪIn the blink of an eye,
everything falls apart笙ｪ

159
00:09:42,520 --> 00:09:45,530
笙ｪBound by the fate we cannot escape笙ｪ

160
00:09:45,700 --> 00:09:50,820
笙ｪYou and I caught in
this tangled love and hate笙ｪ

161
00:09:51,940 --> 00:09:57,130
笙ｪFragile hearts can hardly bear goodbye笙ｪ

162
00:09:58,190 --> 00:10:03,790
笙ｪHow many times
must pain cut deep before we wake?笙ｪ

163
00:10:04,330 --> 00:10:07,710
笙ｪI once gave myself
to you so completely笙ｪ

164
00:10:07,960 --> 00:10:10,909
笙ｪStill holding on to that heart笙ｪ

165
00:10:10,910 --> 00:10:16,049
笙ｪOnly to suffer your fatal blow笙ｪ

166
00:10:16,050 --> 00:10:20,369
笙ｪHow desperately
I long to hold you close笙ｪ

167
00:10:20,370 --> 00:10:22,949
笙ｪYet I approach you with such caution笙ｪ

168
00:10:22,950 --> 00:10:25,229
笙ｪHow could a stand in ever have笙ｪ

169
00:10:25,230 --> 00:10:28,779
笙ｪThe right to be loved by you?笙ｪ

170
00:10:28,780 --> 00:10:33,309
笙ｪIf love is nothing
more than endless schemes笙ｪ

171
00:10:33,310 --> 00:10:35,840
笙ｪUsed and abandoned in the end笙ｪ

172
00:10:35,980 --> 00:10:37,929
笙ｪStill I walk into笙ｪ

173
00:10:37,930 --> 00:10:41,529
笙ｪThe trap you set without regret笙ｪ

174
00:10:41,530 --> 00:10:45,579
笙ｪHow desperately
I long to hold you close笙ｪ

175
00:10:45,580 --> 00:10:48,159
笙ｪYet keep it buried deep inside笙ｪ

176
00:10:48,160 --> 00:10:50,319
笙ｪA stand in can never cross笙ｪ

177
00:10:50,320 --> 00:10:53,759
笙ｪThe shortest distance between us笙ｪ

178
00:10:53,760 --> 00:10:58,730
笙ｪIf love can
make someone lose themselves笙ｪ

179
00:10:58,890 --> 00:11:03,560
笙ｪThen let me stay by your side笙ｪ

180
00:11:06,340 --> 00:11:07,909
笙ｪA substitute笙ｪ

181
00:11:07,910 --> 00:11:12,910
笙ｪNeeds no reason笙ｪ

